{"tid":2500960,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"魔力寶貝正服強勢回歸(54) 標~~~~","createTime":"2021-04-23T04:45:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T05:48:24.000Z","uid":45246,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c4470e018ce94c48423e49485fd2fc8bd3017446","tid":2500960,"uid":45246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MFYQcLZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMFYQcLZ.gif&h=c68c650b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EoCrvXV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEoCrvXV.gif&h=5f6b9af5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f63881a57197ec07476fc0a51b3f5f3a58b852a","tid":2500960,"uid":45246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:45:57.000Z","msg":"永恒初心最精彩片段！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=BScZURkUuMQ&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBScZURkUuMQ%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrX4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=eebf1b58\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=BScZURkUuMQ&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n\t<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n記得拎完獎狀去左邊士兵拎禮包 右邊伏黎<br />\n入雙子 多d hk人<br />\n<br />\nSer已不足一日內玩完（瘋狂斷線）<br />\n電腦game 冇電話版<br />\nMac（<del>所有系統</del>）玩唔到<br />\n<br />\n主程式：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3cvTEox\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3cvTEox&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrX4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=50fcf1bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3cvTEox</a><br />\n<br />\n官網：<a href=\"https://cg.originmood.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcg.originmood.com%2F&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrX4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=8f9f926b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cg.originmood.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://crossgate-memory.herokuapp.com/#/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcrossgate-memory.herokuapp.com%2F%23%2F&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrX4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=49e909ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://crossgate-memory.herokuapp.com/#/</a><br />\n八業巴整既網站<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">要招小圈子請另開新版</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n註冊 link <br />\n右上改名遮電話<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3enqJUU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3enqJUU&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrX4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=83fbb669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3enqJUU</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=211310\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D211310&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrX4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=fb5fa4c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=211310</a><br />\n<br />\n繼承經典內容的《魔力寶貝：永恆初心》2021 年春季上線 採免費制形式推出<br />\n<br />\n熟悉的洗錢內容，支那永恆的騙錢初心，將還給你最經典的斷線《魔力寶貝》，還給你和當年一樣洗錢的感動。不論在哪個世代，bug斷線都會一直陪伴著你。<br />\n<br />\n理想<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf1kqQNNcBJbjAcaFXw9bde3cZoQBQj1VTqftbSYmECMA?filename=a4hd7A5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa4hd7A5.jpg&h=c314716e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現實<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUtPWFutZw1YGaVndFquX9i5Y4TwqdRfD4trAFdP8wzbq?filename=sNnqegu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsNnqegu.png&h=ecf539cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYsSZgjHaBM9Q9P3rSZfS3ULqFbWYv37DEp9p9QQ6KFA7?filename=6yLLega.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yLLega.jpg&h=c17d3f93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><del>以下開返ser先算</del></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果等級不到十級可以去就職領事館找ＮＰＣ可以免費傳送到伊爾村還有聖拉魯卡村（請睇下邊大地圖）<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmc8gYqj6k83mnYEXG3uUPgq3qVVXsbH6HQtm2N6uYUvRv?filename=yahp4tK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyahp4tK.png&h=d7a3d53d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n卡在線的話，在主選單刪除「Assets&gt;data&gt;0-9 folder」即可<br />\n<br />\n解決亂碼<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmX2wuV7Wts7245nzw9KnPCMhFhV9gk3b7VoH9314cWNtY?filename=4NE0CPn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4NE0CPn.png&h=9f262ed2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmaxy3rHUzZCPFPjm5yLzahhbeYZPnBCNDZ8rjca81c1Mt?filename=GOOwKun.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGOOwKun.png&h=1a4b02dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeNwY9foZhiDGsfqgRhgYo2gokVgBtN782G7zzoQFf8Bc?filename=nRQWa9o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnRQWa9o.png&h=45949141&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZa6MML4sProMPm5ws6esaABSrBp1fRpiw2ZRWXqfuuxB?filename=9kqK4uo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9kqK4uo.png&h=5cf82730&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>點樣教大視窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n將電腦既解像度較低<br />\n<br />\n地圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201710/ad03db1a0a037d79f8063e8253656fa1.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201710%2Fad03db1a0a037d79f8063e8253656fa1.JPG&h=a9858ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n揀職可睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=70151&amp;snA=151&amp;bpage=1&amp;ltype=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D70151%26snA%3D151%26bpage%3D1%26ltype%3D&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrX4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%